1. The leading open source automation server, 
2. Jenkins provides hundreds of plugins to support building, deploying and automating any project.
3. Jenkins is a self-contained, open source automation server which can be used to automate all sorts of tasks related to building, testing, and delivering or deploying software.
4. Jenkins can be installed through native system packages, Docker, or even run standalone by any machine with a Java Runtime Environment (JRE) installed
5. We can use this for any CI and CD as it has lots of plugins , which supports various language and cloud providers and OS.
